immigration law and sanctions for hiring illegal aliens 
they were allegedly told to record those duties as 
antismuggling work on their time cards 
us rep jack brooks dtexas and chairman of the house 
government operations committee contends the agents safety was 
threatened when they had to meet employers who may have been hiring 
illegal aliens 
id hate to be an undercover agent traveling around and 
visiting those big employers of aliens theyd recognize you youd 
stand out like a sore thumb brooks said 
but ins commissioner alan nelson said it is ludicrous to 
