widescale resentment and anger about orders issued in february 
that barred his organization and other antiapartheid groups from 
political activity 
president pw bothas government imposed the emergency june 12 
1986 to combat a black uprising against apartheid under which 
south africas 5 million whites control the country and deny its 26 
million blacks a voice in national affairs 
