of the northernbased uganda peoples democratic army but eric 
otema allimadi the rebels leader in exile in london rejected the 
accord in advance 
museveni envoys are trying to negotiate a similar agreement with 
a smaller rebel group fighting in the east the uganda peoples 
army 
