mayor art agnos said wednesday that voters 
refusal to help fend off a projected 180 million budget deficit by 
raising the spending limit will force him to lay off 356 employees 
close three fire stations and cut health services 
i am concerned about it im not frightened by it he said 
of the prospective cuts in public safety and health what people 
