the idea that naval forces are offlimits to arms control talks 
creation of un naval forces of permanent security council 
members and proposed a joint trial in which the member fleets would 
practice maintaining freedom of navigation by un forces 
the united states and many western countries which have naval 
forces in the middle east have opposed a un force as unworkable 
