was a crime committed by people 
the use of force to make people do things is not allowed by 
the uniform code of military justice said lt cmdr larry d 
wynne 
the arguments closed a hearing into the march 2 death of the 
19yearold recruit from appleton wis at the pensacola naval air 
station 
evidence in four days of testimony will be used by cmdr daniel 
j dalesio jr the investigating officer to make a 
recommendation to rear adm david morris chief of naval air 
training in corpus christi texas 
morris has 120 days from the may 10 filing of the formal 
