telecommunications plc three of 16 transponders available on an 
astra satellite due to be launched in november by societe 
europeenne des satellites 
news international also holds an option on a fourth transponder 
the film channel initially will be available only in britain 
while the other channels will be distributed in continental europe 
as well 
